  <entry>
    <title>CLOSE WINDOW SLEEP MODE</title>
    <link href="/2026/07/21/Close-Window-Sleep-Mode/"/>
    <url>/2026/07/21/Close-Window-Sleep-Mode/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="關閉window休眠功能"><a href="#關閉window休眠功能" class="headerlink" title="關閉window休眠功能"></a>關閉window休眠功能</h1><p>關閉休眠功能</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs COPY">powercfg.exe /hibernate off<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>重新啟用休眠功能</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs COPY">powercfg.exe /hibernate on<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
